Available Tools: process_cash | process_card | process_mobile_pay | get_change | refund_transaction
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "amount": number, "currency": "string", "transaction_id": "string" }
Response Schema: { "transaction_id": "string", "status": "string", "change": number, "receipt": "string" }
---
Question: A shopper uses a mobile wallet to pay $4.99 for a fruit cup.
Call: { "func_call": "process_mobile_pay", "amount": 4.99, "currency": "USD", "transaction_id": "VM-2024-1102" }
Response: { "transaction_id": "VM-2024-1102", "status": "approved", "change": 0, "receipt": "RCP-1102-K8" }

